Creative and educational game for children that will help your child spend time with an electronic device effectively. Let your kid feel like a real artist and develop logic skills at the same time. The app includes coloring which is friendly to the youngest and puzzle solving tasks with educational element. Also, the app contains pictures on different topics which will entertain your child with fascinating sounds and funny characters. The following is waiting for you:

- 8 topic packs with 96 puzzles;
- Easy coloring for children;
- Educational puzzles;
- Cute animation in the end of each task.

The app is designed for children of preschool age and also suitable for boys and girls 2- 5 years old. All the activities were developed with participation of experts in the field of children education and include such educational elements as developing of fine motor skills and logic. Have fun!

Educational games for children which will help your baby spend his time with an electronic device effectively. You will visit Bimi Boo’s friends who live on a wondrous island. You will play developing games with a kittens, funny birds and cute squirrel.

The application includes simple games intended to develop fine motor skills and that will entertain your child with bright colors, nice characters and interesting tasks:

- Arrange object by color, form, number and size;
- Use logic when selecting series of items;
- Put geometrical figures on the silhouette;
- Sort things in the right order;
- Restore pictures from memory.

Designed for children of preschool age and also suitable for boys and girls 2- 5 years old. All the activities were developed with participation of experts in the field of children education and include such educational elements as puzzles, sorting and logical games.

The application contains the following developing and educative games for children:

- Items sorting – you need to put food into the fridge and clothes into the wardrobe;
- Logic tasks in the game with a train – help cute kittens get home and deliver food for them;
- Thinking activities where your kid will arrange items in the baskets;
- Logical thinking tasks where your child will sort things by their features.

Bimi Boo with you again! This time you will go to visit friends of Bimi Boo, who live in a treehouse. You will meet a sly cat, funny rabbit and cute squirrel. There is an exciting game in the house of your baby in which he can help to bring order, to place everything in its place and feed friends of Bimi Boo.

15 different games will fascinate a child with not only bright colors and funny animations, but also with interesting and clear tasks such as:

- Arrange items by color, shape, number and size;
- Pick up items within the meaning of;
- Arrange the geometric shapes according to silhouette;
- Sort items in its place
- Feed animals in a right way;
- Restore pictures from memory.

Together with Bimi Boo Shapes & Colors, your baby will learn to distinguish shapes, colors, texture and quantity. The game also improves fine motor skills, attention and intelligence. It contains everything you need for a fun and healthy development of the child.

Avec cette application, vous pouvez apprendre les panneaux routiers en forme de jeu. Notre quiz peut être utile pour les étudiants des auto-écoles qui se préparent à passer les examens pour le permis de conduire, ainsi que les chauffeurs experimentés qui veulent rafraichir le Code de la route dans leur mémoire.

Les avantages de l'application “Panneaux routiers: quiz sur le Code de la route”:

* Deux modes de jeu: quiz avec choix de réponse correcte et mode "Vrai / Faux";
* Possibilité de choisir les catégories des panneaux: on peut choisir les groupes necessaires pour s'entrainer et pour deviner exclusivement les panneaux de ces groupes;
* Deux niveaux de difficulté: le simulateur permet de choisir la quantité de réponses possibles – 4 ou 6. Ca permet de compliquer ou de simplifier le quiz selon vos besoins;
* Statistique après chaque jeu: le simulateur montre la quantité de réponses données et le pourcentage de bonnes réponses parmi les réponses données;
* Ensemble de panneaux routiers au dernier indice de revision de 2021;
* Répertoire complet de panneaux routiers de la France avec descriptions;
* Le fonctionnement de l'application n'exige pas d'accès a Internet;
* L'application est optimisée pour les téléphones ainsi que les tablettes;
* Interface simple et clair.

Are you looking for a fun educational app for your kid to learn the letters of the alphabet? “ABC for Kids” is an all-in-one app for children between 1 and 8 years old that are in kindergarten, in preschool or going to school, and this app will help your kid to learn Portuguese basics. This app helps children develop their vocabulary and their perception of objects and beings.

The Kids will learn in an interactive mode about the:
- Alphabet  - learn the alphabet and the letter pronounciation;
- Numbers - identify numbers from 0 to 9;
- Animals: Domestic Animals, Wild Animals, Aquatic Animals, Birds, Insects - discover the world through beatiful images of animals and their specific sounds;
- Colors - see and learn the basic colors;
- Shapes - explore common recognisable shapes;
- Vegetables - teach kids about the vegetables and how they look;
- Fruits - identify fruits and play with them;
- Transportation - see many of the transportation choices that are available to the mankind;
- Musical Instruments - enjoy the sounds of marvellous musical instruments;
- Flowers - learn what nature has to offer us through colourful flowers;
- Professions - understand the basic jobs such as policeman, soldier, medic,etc.;
- Tools - what tools can be used inside a house? 
- Sports - is your kid going to be a big sports enthusiast? See what sport activities she/he might like;
- Sweets - who doesn’t love a sweet, what does your kid like?
- Objects - explore a list of common objects that kids will lear fast.

The images are accompanied by the pronunciation in the Portuguese language and other specific sounds. 

The voice sounds (female voice) are professionally recorded in studio.

The App has three sections:

1. Learn - browse through the various educational items or let the app play them automatically for you. Kids can press on the images and the corresponding sounds will play.

2. Test - test your skills per each category
Choose between four images in order to find the correct one.

3. Play - test your skills on multiple categories.
Choose between a mix of 16 categories to find one by one the correct items.

The Free app provides access to :
- the Learning Module - Letters, Numbers, Animals
- the Testing Module - Letters, Numbers
- the Game - first two levels of the game

Information personalized to the children’s need of discovery, together with new tests and games will be added periodically to the list of interactive tools. 

You can use the app on all your devices: iPhone, iPad or iPod touch (minimum iOS 5.0 is needed). 

We are parents ourselves, we don’t like it when we see ads in our kids applications, that is why we avoid placing ads them into our apps. Therefore we invite you to support us by purchasing the full version of this app where you will discover a lot of words and games for your kids to start learning the Portuguese basics.

Sound doesn’t work?
Increase the volume and check that your device is not set to Mute . You can find the Mute switch and and the volume buttons on the side of your device.

Thank you for playing our games!
